[{"Code":"en","Title":"Regional Dashboard Onboarding Requirements","Slug":"requirement-per-business-type-regional","ContentType":2,"Content":"<h3 data-block-id=\"me88of4w-x75wx6-040\">General Requirements</h3><p data-block-id=\"mg68zj88-doj6dj-013\">Eligible entities are <strong>Corporations</strong> and <strong>Partnerships</strong>. Sole proprietors and individuals are <span style=\"color:rgb(219, 48, 53)\" type=\"spanMark\"><strong>not allowed.</strong></span></p><p data-block-id=\"me88opyq-m7xumu-041\">Below are the general requirements that we will be needing from entities applying for Regional Dashboard. </p><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appawrVdqjDsPTE4n/shrGkmPHaDU1YuPba\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title=\"\" style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel=\"\" class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p><h3 data-block-id=\"mg6bpfxz-jw0glj-002\">Country Specific Requirements</h3><p data-block-id=\"mg6bpsfn-i6ie1h-003\">Please check the available country options. If the country is not listed, please refer to the general requirements.</p><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appawrVdqjDsPTE4n/shr0tUAwriaFaZQYl\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title=\"\" style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel=\"\" class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p><blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mg6duare-6ghttr-009\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mg6duhmz-drh3om-012\">Note on Documentation:</p></div><p data-block-id=\"mg6duarf-cebys9-010\">We are currently building the database for specific document requirements needed for entities in all countries. For now, we are handling these on a case-by-case basis and will share the file once available. </p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"mgfss0c9-slzh9x-001\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Regional Dashboard Onboarding Requirements","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Persyaratan Onboarding Dasbor Regional","Slug":"requirement-per-business-type-regional","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><h3 data-block-id=\"me88of4w-x75wx6-040\">Persyaratan Umum</h3><p data-block-id=\"mg68zj88-doj6dj-013\">Entitas yang memenuhi syarat adalah <strong>Korporasi</strong> dan <strong>Persekutuan</strong>. Pemilik tunggal dan perorangan <span style=\"color:rgb(219, 48, 53)\" type=\"spanMark\"><strong>tidak diperbolehkan.</strong></span></p><p data-block-id=\"me88opyq-m7xumu-041\">Di bawah ini adalah persyaratan umum yang kami perlukan dari entitas yang mendaftar untuk Regional Dashboard. </p><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appawrVdqjDsPTE4n/shrGkmPHaDU1YuPba\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p><h3 data-block-id=\"mg6bpfxz-jw0glj-002\">Persyaratan Spesifik Negara</h3><p data-block-id=\"mg6bpsfn-i6ie1h-003\">Silakan periksa opsi negara yang tersedia. Jika negara tersebut tidak terdaftar, silakan merujuk pada persyaratan umum.</p><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appawrVdqjDsPTE4n/shr0tUAwriaFaZQYl\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p><blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mg6duare-6ghttr-009\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mg6duhmz-drh3om-012\">Catatan Mengenai Dokumentasi:</p></div><p data-block-id=\"mg6duarf-cebys9-010\">Saat ini kami sedang membangun basis data untuk persyaratan dokumen spesifik yang diperlukan untuk entitas di semua negara. Untuk saat ini, kami menangani hal ini berdasarkan kasus per kasus dan akan membagikan filenya setelah tersedia. </p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"mgfss0c9-slzh9x-001\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Persyaratan Onboarding Dasbor Regional","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"ข้อกำหนดการเริ่มต้นใช้งานแดชบอร์ดระดับภูมิภาค","Slug":"requirement-per-business-type-regional","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><h3 data-block-id=\"me88of4w-x75wx6-040\">ข้อกำหนดทั่วไป</h3><p data-block-id=\"mg68zj88-doj6dj-013\">นิติบุคคลที่มีสิทธิ์คือ <strong>บริษัท</strong> และ <strong>ห้างหุ้นส่วน</strong> เจ้าของกิจการคนเดียวและบุคคลธรรมดา <span style=\"color:rgb(219, 48, 53)\" type=\"spanMark\"><strong>ไม่ได้รับอนุญาต</strong></span></p><p data-block-id=\"me88opyq-m7xumu-041\">ด้านล่างนี้คือข้อกำหนดทั่วไปที่เราต้องการจากนิติบุคคลที่ยื่นขอ Regional Dashboard </p><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appawrVdqjDsPTE4n/shrGkmPHaDU1YuPba\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p><h3 data-block-id=\"mg6bpfxz-jw0glj-002\">ข้อกำหนดเฉพาะประเทศ</h3><p data-block-id=\"mg6bpsfn-i6ie1h-003\">โปรดตรวจสอบตัวเลือกประเทศที่มี หากประเทศนั้นไม่อยู่ในรายการ โปรดดูข้อกำหนดทั่วไป</p><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appawrVdqjDsPTE4n/shr0tUAwriaFaZQYl\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p><blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mg6duare-6ghttr-009\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mg6duhmz-drh3om-012\">หมายเหตุเกี่ยวกับเอกสาร:</p></div><p data-block-id=\"mg6duarf-cebys9-010\">ขณะนี้เรากำลังสร้างฐานข้อมูลสำหรับข้อกำหนดเอกสารเฉพาะที่จำเป็นสำหรับนิติบุคคลในทุกประเทศ สำหรับตอนนี้ เรากำลังจัดการเรื่องเหล่านี้เป็นรายกรณี และจะแชร์ไฟล์ให้เมื่อพร้อมใช้งาน </p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"mgfss0c9-slzh9x-001\"></p>","SeoTitle":"ข้อกำหนดการเริ่มต้นใช้งานแดชบอร์ดระดับภูมิภาค","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Requisitos de Integración del Tablero Regional","Slug":"requirement-per-business-type-regional","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><h3 data-block-id=\"me88of4w-x75wx6-040\">Requisitos Generales</h3><p data-block-id=\"mg68zj88-doj6dj-013\">Las entidades elegibles son <strong>Corporaciones</strong> y <strong>Sociedades</strong>. Los propietarios únicos e individuos <span style=\"color:rgb(219, 48, 53)\" type=\"spanMark\"><strong>no están permitidos.</strong></span></p><p data-block-id=\"me88opyq-m7xumu-041\">A continuación, se presentan los requisitos generales que necesitaremos de las entidades que soliciten el Regional Dashboard. </p><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appawrVdqjDsPTE4n/shrGkmPHaDU1YuPba\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p><h3 data-block-id=\"mg6bpfxz-jw0glj-002\">Requisitos Específicos por País</h3><p data-block-id=\"mg6bpsfn-i6ie1h-003\">Por favor, revise las opciones de país disponibles. Si el país no está en la lista, por favor, consulte los requisitos generales.</p><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appawrVdqjDsPTE4n/shr0tUAwriaFaZQYl\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p><blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mg6duare-6ghttr-009\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mg6duhmz-drh3om-012\">Nota sobre la Documentación:</p></div><p data-block-id=\"mg6duarf-cebys9-010\">Actualmente estamos creando la base de datos para los requisitos de documentos específicos necesarios para las entidades en todos los países. Por ahora, estamos manejando estos casos de forma individual y compartiremos el archivo una vez que esté disponible. </p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"mgfss0c9-slzh9x-001\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Requisitos de Integración del Tablero Regional","Description":null}]